com.serotonin.mango.rt.dataSource.onewire

Class Network

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.serotonin.mango.rt.dataSource.onewire.Network

  • public class Network
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility that can scan a network, and return the network to its pre-scan state. This is important because we can't necessarily tell the difference between relays (that are controlling equipment), and latches (that are serving as branches to other devices).
    Author:
    Matthew Lohbihler
